@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pswobg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v2 / ((v2 + 0.41 * tmp + 0.87) - (v0 + 0.69 + v0 + 0.95)))
    tmp = (v2 + tmp)
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.17 + v0 + 0.62) - 0.76) * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.88) * (tmp + 0.59 - v2 + 0.18)))
    v1 = v0
    v2 = ((v2 - (tmp + 0.58 + tmp + 0.16)) + 0.23)
    tmp = 0.67
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.cos(tmp + 0.85)))
    data[tid] = v0
